# =============================================================================
# Drasi Server Building Comfort - HTTP Requests
# =============================================================================
# Use with the VSCode REST Client extension (humao.rest-client) or similar.
# API documentation is served at http://localhost:8380/api/v1/docs/

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8380
@dashboardUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ==========================================================================
### Health & Info
### ==========================================================================

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List API versions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/versions

### ==========================================================================
### Sources
### ==========================================================================

### List all sources
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sources

### Get the building-facilities source status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sources/building-facilities

### ==========================================================================
### Continuous Queries
### ==========================================================================

### List all queries
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queries

### Per-room comfort levels (the building view feed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queries/building-comfort-ui/results

### Overall building comfort level
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queries/building-comfort-level-calc/results

### Per-floor comfort levels
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queries/floor-comfort-level-calc/results

### Rooms outside the comfortable band (alerts)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queries/room-alert/results

### Floors outside the comfortable band (alerts)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queries/floor-alert/results

### Building outside the comfortable band (alert)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queries/building-alert/results

### ==========================================================================
### Reactions
### ==========================================================================

### List all reactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reactions

### Get the dashboard reaction status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reactions/building-comfort-dashboard

### Open the dashboard in a browser instead: {{dashboardUrl}}
### The seeded "Building Comfort" dashboard is available via the dashboard API:
GET {{dashboardUrl}}/api/dashboards
